<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>ひるでもよるでもとぅるばーる | cafe nora</title>
  <meta name="description" content="2026年8月2日（日）cafe noraにて2公演開催。ひるばーる（開場13:00/開演14:00）・よるばーる（開場17:30/開演18:30）。料金各¥3,000ワンドリンク付。沖縄フードも楽しめる真夏の日曜日。">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/events.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/event-detail.css">
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://cafenora.jp/event-torubale.html">
  <link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.json">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#7a9e7e">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="default">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="cafe nora">
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/images/icon-192.png">
  <script src=https://cdn.onesignal.com/sdks/web/v16/OneSignalSDK.page.js defer></script>
  <script>
    window.OneSignalDeferred = window.OneSignalDeferred || [];
    OneSignalDeferred.push(function(OneSignal) {
      OneSignal.init({
        appId: 'f214c199-2cb9-4e02-90d4-91ca8462d321',
        notifyButton: { enable: false }
      });
    });
  </script>
<style>
  /* とぅるばーる テーマ：沖縄の風・珊瑚と砂浜・縁日の宴 */
  :root {
    --tu-coral: #c4623a;
    --tu-sand: #fdf4e8;
    --tu-teal: #2d6b7e;
    --tu-gold: #d4944a;
  }
  body { background: var(--tu-sand); }
  .section { background-color: var(--tu-sand); }
  .section.bg-warm { background-color: #f5e8d0; }
  .tu-wave { width:100%; margin:2.2rem 0 1.8rem; overflow:hidden; }
  .tu-wave svg { width:100%; display:block; }
  .tu-hib { display:inline-block; width:20px; height:20px; vertical-align:middle; margin-right:.4rem; flex-shrink:0; }
  .tu-hib-lg { display:block; width:52px; height:52px; float:right; margin:0 0 .5rem 1rem; opacity:.5; }
  .tu-san-lg { display:block; float:right; width:34px; height:70px; opacity:.38; margin:0 0 .8rem 1.2rem; }
  .tu-shisa-pair { display:flex; justify-content:center; align-items:center; gap:1.5rem; margin:2rem 0 1rem; }
  .tu-shisa-pair svg { width:38px; height:38px; opacity:.6; }
  .tu-shisa-pair svg:last-child { transform:scaleX(-1); }
  .section-title { color: var(--tu-teal); }
  .section-lead { color: #5a7070; }
  .ed-section-title { color: var(--tu-coral); border-bottom-color: rgba(196,98,58,.25); }
  .ed-text { color: #3d2b1f; }
  .ed-lead-headline { color: var(--tu-teal); font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 3.2vw, 1.65rem); }
  .ed-lead-body { color: #5a4535; }
  .ed-reason-card {
    background: rgba(196,98,58,.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(196,98,58,.2);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .ed-reason-title { color: var(--tu-coral); }
  .ed-reason-desc { color: #5a4535; }
  .ed-meta-table th { color: #7a5a45; font-weight: 400; }
  .ed-meta-table td { color: #3d2b1f; font-weight: 500; }
  .ed-meta-table th,
  .ed-meta-table td { border-bottom-color: rgba(196,98,58,.18); }
  .ed-mid-cta {
    background: rgba(196,98,58,.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(196,98,58,.2);
  }
  .ed-mid-cta-text { color: #7a5a45; }
  .btn-reserve-mid { background: var(--tu-teal); color: #fff; }
  .btn-reserve-mid:hover { opacity: .88; }
  .ed-link-btn { border-color: var(--tu-teal); color: var(--tu-teal); }
  .ed-link-btn:hover { background: var(--tu-teal); color: #fff; border-color: var(--tu-teal); }
  .ed-flyer img { box-shadow: 0 6px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.12); }
  .event-detail-badge.upcoming {
    background: rgba(196,98,58,.1);
    color: var(--tu-coral);
    border: 1px solid rgba(196,98,58,.3);
  }
  .ed-back-link a { color: rgba(45,107,126,.45); }
  .ed-back-link a:hover { color: var(--tu-teal); }
  .reserve-contact-btn {
    background: rgba(45,107,126,.06);
    border-color: rgba(45,107,126,.25);
    color: #3d2b1f;
  }
  .reserve-contact-btn:hover { background: rgba(45,107,126,.1); }
  .reserve-contact-btn .reserve-value { color: var(--tu-teal); }
  .ed-bottom-reserve { border-top-color: rgba(196,98,58,.2); }
  .ed-artist { border-top-color: rgba(196,98,58,.2); }
  .ed-lead { border-top-color: rgba(196,98,58,.15); }
  .ed-reasons { border-top-color: rgba(196,98,58,.15); }
  .ed-urgency-banner { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c4623a, #e8804a); }
  .new-badge { background: var(--tu-coral); }
  .footer { background: #1e3a42; }
  /* フライヤー全体表示ヒーロー */
  .tu-hero-fullflyer {
    position: relative;
    padding: 0 !important;
    background: #1c100a !important;
    min-height: unset !important;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .tu-flyer-img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    opacity: .88;
  }
  .tu-flyer-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom,
      rgba(10,5,0,.08) 0%,
      rgba(10,5,0,.18) 60%,
      rgba(10,5,0,.72) 100%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .tu-hero-fullflyer .ed-hero-content {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  /* ed-top 1カラム化（チラシ削除後） */
  .ed-top { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 560px; }
  .ed-info .event-detail-badge { margin-bottom: .8rem; }

  /* ── 脱AI レイアウト改修 ── */
  /* リード：左寄せ・ボーダーなし */
  .ed-lead { text-align:left; border-top:none; padding-top:1.8rem; }
  .ed-lead-headline { text-align:left; }
  .ed-lead-body { text-align:left; max-width:none; margin:0; }
  /* セクション区切りをワービング（波）に一本化・ボーダー線なし */
  .ed-reasons { border-top:none; padding-top:0; }
  .ed-artist  { border-top:none; }
  .ed-bottom-reserve { border-top:none; }
  /* メタテーブル：値を大きく・ゆったり */
  .ed-meta-table td { font-size:1.05rem; padding:.75rem .5rem; }
  .ed-meta-table th { font-size:.76rem; letter-spacing:.08em; opacity:.65; padding:.75rem .5rem; }
  /* エディトリアル・理由リスト */
  .ed-reasons-list { display:flex; flex-direction:column; margin-top:1.4rem; }
  .ed-reason-item {
    display:flex; gap:1.5rem; align-items:flex-start;
    padding:1.6rem 0;
    border-bottom:1px solid rgba(196,98,58,.12);
  }
  .ed-reason-item:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
  .er-num {
    font-family:var(--font-jp-serif); font-size:2.8rem; font-weight:300;
    color:rgba(196,98,58,.2); line-height:1; flex-shrink:0; width:3rem;
  }
  .er-content { flex:1; }
  .er-icon { font-size:1.4rem; margin-bottom:.3rem; display:block; line-height:1; }
  .er-title { font-weight:700; color:var(--tu-coral); font-size:1rem; margin-bottom:.4rem; line-height:1.5; }
  .er-desc  { font-size:.88rem; color:#5a4535; line-height:1.9; }
  @media(max-width:480px){
    .er-num { font-size:2rem; width:2.4rem; }
  }

</style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="header" id="header">
    <div class="header-inner">
      <div class="header-left"><a href="index.html" class="logo">
        <span class="logo-en">cafe nora</span>
        <span class="logo-jp">カフェ ノラ</span>
      </a><a href="parking.html" class="parking-badge">🚗 臨時駐車場</a></div>
      <button class="menu-btn" id="menuBtn" aria-label="メニューを開く">
        <span></span><span></span><span></span>
      </button>
      <nav class="nav" id="nav">
        <ul class="nav-list">
          <li><a href="index.html">トップ</a></li>
          <li><a href="cafe.html">カフェ</a></li>
          <li><a href="calendar.html">カレンダー</a></li>
          <li><a href="events.html">イベント</a></li>
          <li><a href="popup.html">出店情報</a></li>
          <li><a href="access.html">アクセス</a></li>
          <li><a href="service.html">HP制作</a></li>
          <li><a href="notifications.html">お知らせ</a></li>
          <li><a href="contact.html">お問い合わせ</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>
<script>
  (function(){
    var hdr = document.getElementById('header');
    var hero = document.querySelector('.hero, .gs-hero, .ed-hero, .tu-hero-fullflyer');
    if(hdr && hero){
      hero.style.paddingTop = hdr.offsetHeight + 'px';
      window.addEventListener('resize', function(){
        hero.style.paddingTop = hdr.offsetHeight + 'px';
      });
    }
  })();
</script>

  <!-- ヒーロー -->
  <div class="ed-hero tu-hero-fullflyer">
    <img src="images/torubale-flyer.jpg" alt="ひるでもよるでもとぅるばーる フライヤー" class="tu-flyer-img">
    <div class="tu-flyer-overlay"></div>
    <div class="ed-hero-content">
      <span class="new-badge" style="margin-bottom:.6rem; display:inline-block;">NEW</span>
      <p class="ed-hero-date">2026年 8月 2日（日）</p>
      <h1 class="ed-hero-title">ひるでもよるでも<br><span class="ed-hero-sub">とぅるばーる at cafe nora</span></h1>
      <div class="ed-hero-countdown" id="hero-cd">
        <span>開催まで あと</span>
        <span class="cd-days" id="hero-days">—</span>
        <span>日</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 緊急バナー（残7日以内に表示） -->
  <div class="ed-urgency-banner hidden" id="urgency-banner">
    <span class="ub-text">🎟️ 残席わずか ——「行こうかな」と思っているなら、<br>今日です。</span>
    <a href="https://noratool.pythonanywhere.com/yoyaku" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ub-btn">今すぐ予約する</a>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container ed-container">

      <!-- フライヤー + 基本情報 -->
      <div class="ed-top fade-in">
<div class="ed-info">
          <div class="event-detail-badge upcoming">開催予定</div>
          <table class="ed-meta-table">
            <tr><th>日時</th><td>2026年 8月 2日（日）</td></tr>
            <tr><th>ひるばーる</th><td>開場 13:00 / 開演 14:00<br><small>☀️ cafe nora による「沖縄ぜんざい」販売あり</small></td></tr>
            <tr><th>よるばーる</th><td>開場 17:30 / 開演 18:30<br><small>🌙 真昼の月による「沖縄フード」販売あり</small></td></tr>
            <tr><th>料金</th><td>各 ¥3,000（ワンドリンク付）</td></tr>
            <tr><th>会場</th><td>cafe nora<br><small>愛媛県新居浜市萩生2133-29</small></td></tr>
          </table>
          <div class="ed-mid-cta">
            <p class="ed-mid-cta-text">ひるばーる・よるばーる、どちらも要予約。お早めに。</p>
            <a href="https://noratool.pythonanywhere.com/yoyaku" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-reserve-mid">🎟️ 今すぐ予約する</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 感情リード文 -->
      <div class="ed-lead fade-in">
        <svg class="tu-hib-lg" viewBox="0 0 60 60" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><g transform="translate(30,30)"><ellipse cx="0" cy="-13" rx="7" ry="13" fill="#c4623a" opacity=".7" transform="rotate(0)"/><ellipse cx="0" cy="-13" rx="7" ry="13" fill="#c4623a" opacity=".7" transform="rotate(72)"/><ellipse cx="0" cy="-13" rx="7" ry="13" fill="#c4623a" opacity=".7" transform="rotate(144)"/><ellipse cx="0" cy="-13" rx="7" ry="13" fill="#c4623a" opacity=".7" transform="rotate(216)"/><ellipse cx="0" cy="-13" rx="7" ry="13" fill="#c4623a" opacity=".7" transform="rotate(288)"/><circle cx="0" cy="0" r="4.5" fill="#d4944a"/></g></svg>
        <p class="ed-lead-headline">
          昼でも、夜でも——<br>真夏の日曜日はとぅるばーる。
        </p>
        <p class="ed-lead-body">
          8月2日（日）、cafe noraに沖縄の風が吹きます。<br><br>
          昼の部「ひるばーる」では沖縄ぜんざい、夜の部「よるばーる」では真昼の月の沖縄フードも。2公演限りの特別な一日。<br><br>
          片方だけでも、はしごしても。夏の思い出になる時間が、ここにあります。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 3つの理由（後で更新） -->
      <div class="tu-wave" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 800 22" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none">
          <path d="M0 11 Q100 3 200 11 Q300 19 400 11 Q500 3 600 11 Q700 19 800 11" stroke="#2d6b7e" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" opacity=".4"/>
          <path d="M0 15 Q100 7 200 15 Q300 23 400 15 Q500 7 600 15 Q700 23 800 15" stroke="#c4623a" fill="none" stroke-width="1" opacity=".3"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="ed-reasons fade-in">
        <h2 class="ed-section-title"><svg class="tu-hib" viewBox="0 0 40 40" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><g transform="translate(20,20)"><ellipse cx="0" cy="-9" rx="5" ry="9" fill="#c4623a" opacity=".8" transform="rotate(0)"/><ellipse cx="0" cy="-9" rx="5" ry="9" fill="#c4623a" opacity=".8" transform="rotate(72)"/><ellipse cx="0" cy="-9" rx="5" ry="9" fill="#c4623a" opacity=".8" transform="rotate(144)"/><ellipse cx="0" cy="-9" rx="5" ry="9" fill="#c4623a" opacity=".8" transform="rotate(216)"/><ellipse cx="0" cy="-9" rx="5" ry="9" fill="#c4623a" opacity=".8" transform="rotate(288)"/><circle cx="0" cy="0" r="3" fill="#d4944a"/></g></svg>この日に来るべき、3つの理由</h2>
        <div class="ed-reasons-list">
          <div class="ed-reason-item">
            <span class="er-num">01</span>
            <div class="er-content">
              <span class="er-icon">☀️🌙</span>
              <p class="er-title">昼と夜、2回楽しめる</p>
              <p class="er-desc">ひるばーる（14:00開演）・よるばーる（18:30開演）の2部制。片方だけでも、両方はしごしても。一日中とぅるばーるに浸れます。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="ed-reason-item">
            <span class="er-num">02</span>
            <div class="er-content">
              <span class="er-icon">🍧</span>
              <p class="er-title">沖縄フードも楽しめる</p>
              <p class="er-desc">昼の部ではcafe noraが「沖縄ぜんざい」を、夜の部では真昼の月が「沖縄フード」を販売。音楽とともに沖縄気分を味わえます。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="ed-reason-item">
            <span class="er-num">03</span>
            <div class="er-content">
              <span class="er-icon">🏖️</span>
              <p class="er-title">真夏の日曜日、限りの出会い</p>
              <p class="er-desc">8月2日だけの特別な2公演。新居浜の小さなカフェで過ごす、夏の特別な一日をぜひ。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- アーティスト紹介（後で更新） -->
      <div class="tu-wave" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 800 22" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none">
          <path d="M0 11 Q100 3 200 11 Q300 19 400 11 Q500 3 600 11 Q700 19 800 11" stroke="#2d6b7e" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" opacity=".4"/>
          <path d="M0 15 Q100 7 200 15 Q300 23 400 15 Q500 7 600 15 Q700 23 800 15" stroke="#c4623a" fill="none" stroke-width="1" opacity=".3"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="ed-artist fade-in"><svg class="tu-san-lg" viewBox="0 0 28 58" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="10" y="1" width="8" height="10" rx="1.5" fill="#c4623a"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="3" r="1.8" fill="#d4944a"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="7" r="1.8" fill="#d4944a"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="11" r="1.8" fill="#d4944a"/><rect x="9" y="11" width="10" height="2" rx="0.5" fill="#d4944a"/><rect x="12" y="13" width="4" height="29" rx="2" fill="#c4623a"/><circle cx="14" cy="49" r="9" fill="#c4623a"/><circle cx="14" cy="49" r="3.5" fill="rgba(0,0,0,.18)"/><rect x="10.5" y="46" width="7" height="2" rx="1" fill="#d4944a"/><line x1="12.5" y1="13" x2="11" y2="46" stroke="rgba(255,220,140,.6)" stroke-width=".6"/><line x1="14" y1="13" x2="14" y2="46" stroke="rgba(255,220,140,.6)" stroke-width=".6"/><line x1="15.5" y1="13" x2="17" y2="46" stroke="rgba(255,220,140,.6)" stroke-width=".6"/></svg>
        <h2 class="ed-section-title"><svg class="tu-hib" viewBox="0 0 40 40" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><g transform="translate(20,20)"><ellipse cx="0" cy="-9" rx="5" ry="9" fill="#c4623a" opacity=".8" transform="rotate(0)"/><ellipse cx="0" cy="-9" rx="5" ry="9" fill="#c4623a" opacity=".8" transform="rotate(72)"/><ellipse cx="0" cy="-9" rx="5" ry="9" fill="#c4623a" opacity=".8" transform="rotate(144)"/><ellipse cx="0" cy="-9" rx="5" ry="9" fill="#c4623a" opacity=".8" transform="rotate(216)"/><ellipse cx="0" cy="-9" rx="5" ry="9" fill="#c4623a" opacity=".8" transform="rotate(288)"/><circle cx="0" cy="0" r="3" fill="#d4944a"/></g></svg>とぅるばーるとは</h2>
        <p class="ed-text">
          沖縄の言葉で「どちらでも」を意味する「とぅるばーる」。<br>
          昼でも夜でも、どちらでもいい——そんな自由で温かい音楽の空気をcafe noraへ届けてくれます。<br>
          ギターと三線（さんしん）の音色が溶け合う、唯一無二のライブをお楽しみください。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 下部予約 -->

      <div class="tu-shisa-pair" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 44 44" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><ellipse cx="22" cy="37" rx="13" ry="7" fill="#2d6b7e" opacity=".85"/><circle cx="22" cy="21" r="14" fill="#2d6b7e" opacity=".85"/><polygon points="10,13 7,3 17,10" fill="#2d6b7e" opacity=".85"/><polygon points="34,13 37,3 27,10" fill="#2d6b7e" opacity=".85"/><circle cx="16" cy="20" r="3" fill="white"/><circle cx="28" cy="20" r="3" fill="white"/><circle cx="17" cy="20" r="1.5" fill="#1a2a30"/><circle cx="29" cy="20" r="1.5" fill="#1a2a30"/><ellipse cx="22" cy="26" rx="2.5" ry="2" fill="#1d4f5e"/><path d="M13 30 Q22 38 31 30" fill="#c4623a" opacity=".75"/><rect x="18" y="30" width="3" height="3" rx=".5" fill="white"/><rect x="23" y="30" width="3" height="3" rx=".5" fill="white"/></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 44 44" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><ellipse cx="22" cy="37" rx="13" ry="7" fill="#2d6b7e" opacity=".85"/><circle cx="22" cy="21" r="14" fill="#2d6b7e" opacity=".85"/><polygon points="10,13 7,3 17,10" fill="#2d6b7e" opacity=".85"/><polygon points="34,13 37,3 27,10" fill="#2d6b7e" opacity=".85"/><circle cx="16" cy="20" r="3" fill="white"/><circle cx="28" cy="20" r="3" fill="white"/><circle cx="17" cy="20" r="1.5" fill="#1a2a30"/><circle cx="29" cy="20" r="1.5" fill="#1a2a30"/><ellipse cx="22" cy="26" rx="2.5" ry="2" fill="#1d4f5e"/><path d="M13 30 Q22 38 31 30" fill="#c4623a" opacity=".75"/><rect x="18" y="30" width="3" height="3" rx=".5" fill="white"/><rect x="23" y="30" width="3" height="3" rx=".5" fill="white"/></svg></div>
      <div class="ed-bottom-reserve fade-in">
